<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Quantaa.net - Compute Intelligence Innovation</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #03050a;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
      --panel-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
      --text: #ffffff;
      --muted: #b7c0d4;
      --blue: #0077ff;
      --cyan: #00d4ff;
      --purple: #8a2be2;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 22%, rgba(0, 119, 255, 0.14), transparent 26%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 22%, rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.16), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 100%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.08), transparent 35%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -2;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 48px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      background: rgba(3, 5, 10, 0.88);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .nav {
      min-height: 82px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .logo img {
      height: 40px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 34px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }

    nav a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: var(--cyan);
    }

    .cta {
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.85);
      border-right-color: rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.95);
      border-bottom-color: rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.95);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 26px rgba(0, 119, 255, 0.16);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 560px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(3,5,10,0.98) 0%, rgba(3,5,10,0.74) 36%, rgba(3,5,10,0.50) 100%),
        url("public/images/backgrounds/quantaa-hero-background.png");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center right;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(3,5,10,0.78) 100%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 72% 48%, transparent 0%, rgba(3,5,10,0.22) 38%, rgba(3,5,10,0.82) 82%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 520px;
      padding: 80px 0;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 26px;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 76px);
      line-height: 1.05;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.045em;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      display: block;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffffff, var(--cyan), var(--purple));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      text-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.18);
    }

    .hero p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin: 0 0 34px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.72);
      border-right-color: rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.82);
      border-bottom-color: rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.82);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      background: rgba(3,5,10,0.48);
    }

    section {
      padding: 70px 0;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.45fr;
      gap: 60px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      color: var(--cyan);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0 0 22px;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 48px);
      line-height: 1.18;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .lead {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.75;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 34px 28px;
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--panel);
      box-shadow: 0 0 42px rgba(0, 119, 255, 0.08);
      min-height: 210px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .icon {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      margin: 0 auto 24px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.46);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-size: 28px;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 26px rgba(0, 119, 255, 0.16);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .stats {
      margin-top: 38px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
    }

    .stat:last-child {
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .number {
      font-size: 38px;
      color: var(--cyan);
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--blue), var(--purple));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 34px 0;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.48);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav ul {
        display: none;
      }

      .split {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .cards,
      .stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .stat {
        border-right: 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      }

      .stat:last-child {
        border-bottom: 0;
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 620px;
        background-position: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="logo" href="/" aria-label="Quantaa.net home">
        <img src="public/images/quantaa-logo-main.png" alt="Quantaa.net logo">
      </a>

      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="#solutions">Solutions</a></li>
          <li><a href="#technology">Technology</a></li>
          <li><a href="#industries">Industries</a></li>
          <li><a href="style-guide.html">Style Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>

      <a class="cta" href="#contact">Get Started →</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>
            Compute.
            <span>Intelligence.</span>
            <span>Innovation.</span>
          </h1>
          <p>
            Quantaa delivers cutting-edge AI solutions powered by advanced compute
            infrastructure and intelligent networking technologies.
          </p>
          <a class="button" href="#solutions">Explore Solutions →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="container split">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">About Quantaa</div>
          <h2>Pioneering the Future of AI Infrastructure</h2>
          <p class="lead">
            At Quantaa, we build the intelligent foundation for tomorrow. Our advanced
            computing and networking solutions help businesses unlock the full potential
            of their data, automation, and AI operations.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="cards" id="solutions">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">▣</div>
            <h3>Advanced Compute</h3>
            <p>High-performance infrastructure designed for AI workloads at scale.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">⌬</div>
            <h3>Intelligent Networking</h3>
            <p>Low-latency, high-throughput networks optimized for the future.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">◌</div>
            <h3>AI Innovation</h3>
            <p>Practical AI systems that drive real-world business outcomes.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="number">10+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Years of Innovation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="number">500+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">AI Workflows</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="number">99.99%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Uptime Reliability</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <div class="number">24/7</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Expert Support</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      © 2026 Quantaa.net. Compute • Intelligence • Innovation.
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
